        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2020-05-26 22:09:16.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review+1\n\nI have a question the counterpart changes on drools-applications that were already submitted, if I remember correctly was using JPA in java:   \n\nDo you think those changes would be compatible with a database that was created in Frankfurt, but for a drools-applications image from guilin?    The concern is trying to avoid the issue that API experiences with no being able to use database from previous release.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
